{
  "stem": "3360.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You could come into the-- into the-- into the United States with an affidavit properly executed here, in the United States, by a blood relation who had the financial wherewithals to support you, or your family, or whoever, until such time as you could make your own way, so that nobody should fall in-- fall onto the state and be-- so that the state-- the United States would not be liable for supporting anybody, keeping anybody alive.",
      "word_count": 77
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right, so on that morning, which was the morning of the 10th or 11th of November, 1938, I was walking to school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't have a telephone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a lot of people didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the streets were unusually quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were some women who were walking outside, crying, beside themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, I remember at least two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it looked like they were still in their nightclothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, normally, you know, in Germany, which is a very formal country, [LAUGHS] you don't see that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I arrived at the school, there was, was really next to nobody there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we were told that there would be no school and that during the night, the government had arrested a lot of Jewish men, that a lot of things had been set on fire, destroyed, and-- the stores, the businesses.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it, it was an attack, supposedly, in response to the shooting of this minor official in Paris by this young, Polish Jew.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was-- it was, in effect, an ordered response by the SA and the SS.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the smaller towns, as it was throughout the Nazi period, it was always much worse because everybody knew who you were.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
